Package: stone
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: stone-mgr (= ${binary:Version}),
         stone-mon (= ${binary:Version}),
         stone-osd (= ${binary:Version}),
Recommends: stone-mds (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: distributed storage and file system
 Stone is a massively scalable, open-source, distributed
 storage system that runs on commodity hardware and delivers object,
 block and file system storage.

