Package: stonefs-shell
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
         ${python3:Depends}
Description: interactive shell for the Stone distributed file system
 Stone is a massively scalable, open-source, distributed
 storage system that runs on commodity hardware and delivers object,
 block and file system storage.  This is an interactive tool that
 allows accessing a Stone file system without mounting it by providing
 a nice pseudo-shell which works like an FTP client.
 .
 This package contains a CLI for interacting with the StoneFS.

